1. Ova *predavanja* su veoma zanimljiva. (These *lectures* are very interesting.)
2. Profesor je odložio *predavanja* za sutra. (The professor postponed the *lectures* for tomorrow.)
3. Studenti su čekali ispred amfiteatra za početak *predavanja*. (The students were waiting outside the lecture hall for the start of the *lectures*.)
4. Ona nikada ne propušta *predavanja*. (She never misses *lectures*.)
5. Prošle nedelje smo imali gostujuća *predavanja* iz Francuske. (Last week we had guest *lectures* from France.)
6. Danas smo u *predavanjima* učili o novim tehnologijama. (Today we learned about new technologies in *lectures*.)
7. *Predavanja* su mi najdraži deo studiranja. (Lectures are my favorite part of studying.)
8. Moram se pripremiti za *predavanje* koje ću održati sledeće sedmice. (I have to prepare for the *lecture* that I will give next week.)
9. Završio je svoje *predavanje* i pozvao studente da postavljaju pitanja. (He finished his *lecture* and invited students to ask questions.)
10. Naš fakultet organizuje *predavanja* iz oblasti preduzetništva i inovacija. (Our faculty organizes *lectures* in the fields of entrepreneurship and innovation.)